transcripts: Bring your Gold's Gym strength training home with the xrs 20 Olympic track and bench. Built by the professionals, now you can access all your favorite strength stations from the convenience of your home. Whether you're a beginner or experienced lifter, you'll appreciate the Olympic width so you can take your training as far as you want. Easily adjust the sturdy metal uprights to accommodate multiple lists for any of the bench positions. Choose from flat, incline, and decline for truly versatile training. The role preacher pad helps you protect your curl and ensure proper form and the built-in squat rack keeps your weight safe and secure throughout each movement. The adjustable safety spotters also help prevent injury if you fail during a lift. When you're ready to utilize the leg developer station, simply remove the crow yoke challenge those lower body muscles by placing weight plates on the leg developer to really take your work out to the extreme. The XR 20 features plate storage to keep your home gym free of clutter. Gold's Gym brings you over 50 years of expertise with the included exercise chart. Each movement helps you target specific muscles while also keeping your overall physique balanced. Choose the brand lifters trust with the gold's gym xrs 20 Olympic track and bench.
